{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/momentum","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"momentum이-뭔데\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#momentum%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AD%94%EB%8D%B0\" aria-label=\"momentum이 뭔데 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Momentum이 뭔데?</h2>\n<p>아는 사람은 아는 생산성 익스텐션이다. 정보의 홍수에 지친 우리네 사람들이 하나에만 집중할 수 있도록, 크롬을 켜면 네이버나 구글이 아니라 아래 페이지로 시작한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5925925925926%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/3e767/example.webp 270w,\n/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/9e625/example.webp 540w,\n/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/0ba47/example.webp 640w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/6f81f/example.jpg 270w,\n/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/09d21/example.jpg 540w,\n/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/c08c5/example.jpg 640w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/70cef47d5ac4b73faabacf7128edc009/c08c5/example.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Momentum 익스텐션\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>물론 웹을 잘 알지도 못하는 내가 독창적으로 이걸 클론코딩해보자는 기특한 생각을 하진 않았겠고, 노마드 코더의 <a href=\"https://nomadcoders.co/javascript-for-beginners\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">바닐라 JS로 크롬 앱 만들기</a> 강의에서 하길래 한번 해봤다. 필자는 위 강의에 더하여 구글 검색, 뽀모도로 타이머 기능을 추가했다. <a href=\"https://yoopark.github.io/nomad-vanila-js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">여기</a>에 배포해두었으니 참고 바란다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1080px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.81481481481482%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/3e767/result.webp 270w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/9e625/result.webp 540w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/260c2/result.webp 1080w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/7509d/result.webp 1620w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/b45a4/result.webp 1675w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/01bf6/result.png 270w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/07484/result.png 540w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/302a4/result.png 1080w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/0d292/result.png 1620w,\n/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/567ac/result.png 1675w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ff3951977776ccdc2a40aea53c13a708/302a4/result.png\"\n            alt=\"결과물 사진\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"features\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#features\" aria-label=\"features permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>localStorage를 활용한 Todo CRUD</li>\n<li>25분(1뽀모도로) 타이머</li>\n<li>현재 시각(Date), 현재 날씨(OpenWeatherMap API) 표시</li>\n<li>랜덤 배경, 랜덤 명언</li>\n<li>구글에 검색하는 Input</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"til\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#til\" aria-label=\"til permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TIL</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-bem-네이밍-컨벤션\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-bem-%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%B4%EB%B0%8D-%EC%BB%A8%EB%B2%A4%EC%85%98\" aria-label=\"1 bem 네이밍 컨벤션 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. BEM 네이밍 컨벤션</h3>\n<p>Block-Element-Modifier의 약자로 HTML 클래스명 지을 때 주로 쓴다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.block__element--modifier</code> 형식으로 작성한다.<br>\n예) <code class=\"language-text\">contact-form__button-submit--03_disable</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-시맨틱-태그\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%8B%9C%EB%A7%A8%ED%8B%B1-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8\" aria-label=\"2 시맨틱 태그 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 시맨틱 태그</h3>\n<p>SEO 최적화, 웹 접근성 향상, 코드 가독성을 위해 반드시 써야 한다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.semrush.com/blog/uploads/media/cc/85/cc85d452a743e27f68d426df35e4da7d/original.png\" alt=\"semantic-tag\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-defer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-defer\" aria-label=\"3 defer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. defer</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>head에 그냥 script 추가 : HTML은 파싱 중 마주치는 순서대로 block한 뒤 fetch &#x26; execute 하기 때문에 body 위에 하는 건 좋지 않다.</li>\n<li>body 안 끝 부분에 script 추가 : body를 빨리 볼 수는 있지만 JS 의존이 큰 페이지라면 비정상적으로 작동한다고 느낄 것이다.</li>\n<li>head에 async : HTML 파싱과 병렬로 fetch한 뒤 execute할 때만 HTML 파싱을 block한다. 하지만 파싱되기도 전에 querySelector 같은게 실행될 수도 있고 먼저 fetch 완료된 것부터 실행되기 때문에 JS 간 실행 순서도 보장할 수 없다.</li>\n<li>head에 defer : fetch까지는 async와 똑같지만 execute를 파싱 완료 시점으로 지연시키고, JS가 작성된 순서대로 실행시킨다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"4-flexbox\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-flexbox\" aria-label=\"4 flexbox permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Flexbox</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>flex-direction</li>\n<li>justify-contents &#x26; align-items</li>\n<li>flex-basis &#x26; flex-grow &#x26; flex-shrink</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"기타\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80\" aria-label=\"기타 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기타</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>localStorage set &#x26; get</li>\n<li>setInterval &#x26; clearInterval</li>\n<li>fetch (Promise)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"소감\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%90\" aria-label=\"소감 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>소감</h2>\n<p>Momentum 익스텐션이랑 너무 똑같게 만드는데 집중하느라 오히려 창의성이 부족했다. <a href=\"https://nomadcoders.co/faq/challenge/vanillajs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">여기</a>에 들어가보면, 같은 기능이지만 얼마나 다양한 디자인이 나올 수 있는지 감탄할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>팀 개발을 하고 싶지만, 군대라 그럴 수 없어 너무 아쉽다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Momentum 익스텐션 클론코딩","date":"July 23, 2022","categories":["JavaScript"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/momentum"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}